        subtitle: "Помните о 5 пониженных доменах",
        text: "<strong style='color:var(--gold);font-size:1.5rem'>R</strong>isk of bias — Can we trust the studies?<br><br><strong style='color:var(--gold);font-size:1.5rem'>I</strong>nconsistency — Do studies agree?<br><br><strong style='color:var(--gold);font-size:1.5rem'>I</strong>ndirectness — Does evidence match our question?<br><br><strong style='color:var(--gold);font-size:1.5rem'>I</strong>mprecision — Is the estimate precise?<br><br><strong style='color:var(--gold);font-size:1.5rem'>P</strong>ublication bias — Is evidence missing?",
